title: Hero Hindustani
subTitle: A young woman conspires with a man to fake a relationship, outsmarting her grandfather's plans to marry her off to a stranger.

title: Prem Deewane

subTitle: A dynastic struggle between the collateral branches of the Kuru clan, the Kauravas and Pandavas, for the throne of Hastinapur leads to the Kurukshetra War.

title: Akhanda
subTitle: When the nefarious Varadarajulu plans to attack Murali Krishna, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, Akhanda leaves no stone unturned to defeat the evil.

title: Krrish
subTitle: After discovering his father's truth, Krrish must reveals his superpowers to the world and becomes the masked superhero.

subTitle: Ajay, a commando, is forced to kidnap Anita, the home minister's daughter, to free his girlfriend Neha from the clutches of terrorists. In the process, he uncovers a shocking revelation.

title: Ram Lakhan
subTitle: Ram, an upright police officer, and his brother Lakhan, a playboy, vow vengeance when they learn that their father was killed by two wicked tricksters.

title: Hum Hain Kamaal Ke
subTitle: Two men with hearing and speech impairments run a grocery store. When a man is murdered in their store by an underworld gang who are after stolen diamonds, they try their hand at solving the case.

title: Indian
subTitle: Police officer Raj Azad arrests terrorist Wasim Khan and prepares to interrogate him. However, his father-in-law mysteriously dies, after which he is blamed for his death and goes on the run.

subTitle: When his parents are killed by three men, Amar, Akbar and Anthony, Vijay teams up with a forest officer who was framed in a murder case to avenge their deaths.

title: Mohalla Assi

title: S 3

title: Mard

title: Main Tera Dushman
